gobblin.cluster

Class GobblinTaskStateModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.helix.participant.statemachine.StateModel
      • org.apache.helix.task.TaskStateModel
        • gobblin.cluster.GobblinTaskStateModel

  • @Alpha
public class GobblinTaskStateModel
extends org.apache.helix.task.TaskStateModel
    A state model for a Gobblin task that implements all supported state transitions.

    This class is currently not used but may get used in the future if we decide to plugin our own custom TaskStateModel. So currently this is like a place holder class.
